de.oaam.model.oaam.restrictions

Interface RestrictionsContainerA

  • All Superinterfaces:
    org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject, org.eclipse.emf.common.notify.Notifier, OaamBaseElementA
    All Known Subinterfaces:
    Restrictions, Subrestrictions
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    RestrictionsContainerAImpl, RestrictionsImpl, SubrestrictionsImpl

    public interface RestrictionsContainerA
extends OaamBaseElementA
    A representation of the model object 'Container A'. The root element of the restrictions model.

    The following features are supported:

    • Device Type Restrictions
    • Device Restrictions
    • Location Restrictions
    • Area Restrictions
    • Power Source Restrictions
    • Task Atomic Restrictions
    • Task Symmetry Restrictions
    • Synchronicity Restriction
    • Connection Restrictions
    • Connection Type Restrictions
    • Segregation Restrictions
    • Subrestrictions
    • Time Delay Restrictions
    See Also:
    RestrictionsPackage.getRestrictionsContainerA()
